com.canoo.dolphin.client.javafx.binding

Class FXWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.canoo.dolphin.client.javafx.binding.FXWrapper

  • public class FXWrapper
extends Object
    A util class that can be used to create JavaFX properties and lists as wrapper around Dolphin Platform properties and lists.
